Usage: setRailPrototypeMode [-help] [-reset] [-domain <list>]
                            [-railModel {virtual|existing}]
                            [-totalPower <value>]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-reset                            # Resets all or specified options to default value
-domain <list>                    # Format: -domain {{PD1 <value1> net1} {PD2
                                  # <value2> net2}..} (string, default="")
-railModel {virtual|existing}     # Seletc rail model: virtual/existing.
                                  # (enums={virtual existing}, default=existing)
-totalPower <value>               # total power defined by user.
                                  # (float, default=0)